  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is:&#xD;
&#xD;
        -  To evaluate risk factors for cancers of the biliary tract by registering new patients&#xD;
           and their counterparts in a multi-center program&#xD;
&#xD;
        -  Development of programs by creating a multi-center biliary tract cancer registration&#xD;
           system&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
